abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种地理测绘专用的便于安装的经纬仪，包括固定座，还包括调节组件和夹紧组件，所述调节组件由限位轴、旋转架、限位块A、支撑块、通槽、螺杆和限位盘组成，所述固定座底部设置有三组限位轴，所述限位轴上安装有旋转架，所述旋转架底部安装有限位块A，所述限位块A内开设有通槽，所述通槽内插接有限位块A，所述限位块A侧壁安装有限位盘，所述限位盘内插接有螺杆。本实用新型通过夹紧组件，便于快速对经纬仪主体进行安装与拆卸，通过调节组件，调节支撑块的位置，从而调节经纬仪主体的测绘高度。

title_localized.text: Novel boiler
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a novel boiler, including the boiler body, the upper cover is installed to boiler body upper end, and the upper cover includes interior head and outer head, and outer head threaded connection is on boiler body upper end surface, and interior head welds with the boiler body upper end, and the inner cover is installed at outer head inner chamber in the interior head, the inner chamber lower part and the combustion chamber intercommunication of interior head, and upper portion and the pipe intercommunication of discharging fume, and the radiator is installed in the boiler body outside, and the hot water inlet of radiator passes through the inlet tube and is connected with the hot water delivery port of boiler body. The utility model discloses a space that the outer head intracavity lies in between baffle below and the interior head outside forms a cold water inlet and the delivery port between the water channel for the high temperature flue gas that the boiler discharged when the upper cover with cross heat exchange between the cold water in the water channel, make the waste heat of high temperature flue gas obtain retrieving, the stop of having avoided the high temperature flue gas makes whole fuselage temperature high on the high side and causes equipment to damage easily, life shortens.

title_localized.text: 一种新型锅炉
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种新型锅炉，包括锅炉本体，锅炉本体上端安装有上封头，上封头包括内封头和外封头，外封头螺纹连接在锅炉本体上端表面，内封头与锅炉本体上端焊接，且内封头安装在外封头内腔，内封头的内腔下部与燃烧室连通，且上部与排烟管连通，锅炉本体外侧安装有散热器，散热器的热水进水口通过进水管与锅炉本体的热水出水口连接。本实用新型通过外封头内腔内位于隔板下方与内封头外侧之间的空隙形成一个冷水进水口与出水口之间的过水通道，使得锅炉排放的高温烟气经过上封头时与过水通道内的冷水之间热量交换，使得高温烟气的余热得到回收，避免了高温烟气的停留使得整个机身温度偏高而造成设备容易损坏，使用寿命缩短。
inventor_harmonized.name: YANG YANZHONG

title_localized.text: Long-term effect simulation experiment device of engineering barrier and surrounding rock of adjustable crack form
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses an engineering barrier and surrounding rock long-term action simulation experiment device capable of adjusting crack forms, wherein a reaction cavity is arranged in an environment simulation cabin, permeable stones are arranged at the bottom of the reaction cavity, a gas filtering plug is pressed at the top of the reaction cavity through a top cover, a water inlet channel connected with the bottom surface of the permeable stones is arranged at the bottom of the environment simulation cabin, and the water inlet channel is connected with a water supply system; a plurality of detection points are distributed on the outer side wall of the reaction cavity, and a heater is arranged on the outer side of the reaction cavity; a preset gap communicated with the reaction cavity is formed on the side wall of the environment simulation cabin; the crack simulation mechanism is in sealed butt joint with the preset gap, the crack simulation mechanism is provided with a groove bottom plate and a glass upper plate which are in up-and-down butt joint, and the groove bottom plate and the glass upper plate are in butt joint to form a simulation crack communicated with the lower part of the reaction cavity; the monitoring system comprises a sensor arranged on a detection point and a camera arranged above the upper glass plate, the sensor is electrically connected with the data recorder, and the data recorder and the camera are electrically connected with the computer.
inventor_harmonized.name: BIAN XIA
assignee: 河海大学

title_localized.text: 可调节裂缝形态的工程屏障与围岩长期作用模拟实验装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种可调节裂缝形态的工程屏障与围岩长期作用模拟实验装置，环境模拟舱内部具有反应腔，反应腔底部具有透水石、顶部通过顶盖压紧有气体过滤塞，环境模拟舱底部具有与透水石底面连接的进水通道，进水通道连接有供水系统；反应腔外侧壁分布有多个检测点，反应腔外侧安装有加热器；环境模拟舱侧壁形成有与反应腔连通的预设缺口；裂缝模拟机构与预设缺口密封对接，裂缝模拟机构具有上下对接的凹槽底板和玻璃上板，凹槽底板和玻璃上板对接形成与反应腔下部连通的模拟裂缝；监控系统包括安装在检测点上的传感器，以及布置在玻璃上板上方的摄像机，传感器均与数据记录器电性连接，数据记录器和摄像机均与计算机电性连接。
inventor_harmonized.name: LIU KEYU

title_localized.text: Server board card heat dissipation device and server board card
abstract_localized.text: The disclosure relates to the field of heat dissipation of processors of servers, and provides a server board card heat dissipation device and a server board card; the server board card heat dissipation device comprises a thermoelectric conversion module, a fan and a heat dissipation component, and the server board card further comprises a processor, a circuit board and a bottom plate; one surface of the thermoelectric conversion module is used for being attached to the processor, the thermoelectric conversion module is electrically connected with the fan, and an air outlet of the fan is arranged opposite to the heat dissipation part; the thermoelectric conversion module is used for converting heat emitted by the processor into electric energy so as to drive the fan, so that wind flow generated by the work of the fan is blown to the heat dissipation part, and the heat dissipation of the heat dissipation part is accelerated; the heat dissipation component is arranged to dissipate heat which is not absorbed by the thermoelectric conversion module; thus realizing double heat dissipation effect, improving heat dissipation efficiency, realizing reutilization of heat energy, the heat released to the nature is reduced, and the method is green, energy-saving, low-carbon and environment-friendly.
inventor_harmonized.name: WANG LISHENG
assignee: 上海闻泰电子科技有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: SHANGHAI WINGTECH ELECTRONICS TECHNOLOGY CO LTD

title_localized.text: 服务器板卡散热装置及服务器板卡
abstract_localized.text: 本公开涉及服务器的处理器散热领域，提供一种服务器板卡散热装置及服务器板卡；服务器板卡散热装置包括热电转化模组、风扇和散热部件，服务器板卡还包括处理器、电路板和底板；热电转化模组的一面用于贴附在处理器上，热电转化模组与风扇电连接，风扇的出风口与散热部件相对设置；热电转化模组用于将处理器散发的热量转化为电能，以驱动风扇，使风扇工作产生的风流吹向散热部件，加速散热部件的散热；通过设置散热部件，对未被热电转化模组吸收的热量进行散热；这样就实现了双重散热的效果，提高了散热效率，还实现了热能的再利用，减少了释放到大自然的热量，绿色节能、低碳环保。
inventor_harmonized.name: MENG XIN

title_localized.text: 一种热敷理疗护理装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及理疗护理技术领域，且公开了一种热敷理疗护理装置，包括固定框，所述固定框的内壁滑动连接有可存放工具的储存机构，所述固定框的顶部固定连接有便于调整本装置高度的液压杆，所述液压杆的顶部固定连接有横板，所述横板的内部设置有夹层，夹层的内部固定连接有驱动机构；本实用新型通过按动机构的设置，在使用本装置对患处进行热敷时，还可以对患处进行按摩，松弛患处紧张的肌肉，加速缓解患处疼痛的情况，同时按动机构还可以对热敷袋进行加热，避免热敷袋在长时间使用后温度降低，提高热敷的效果，解决了目前对患处进行热敷，无法对患处的肌肉进行松弛，且热敷袋在使用时温度不断降低，热敷效果差的问题。

title_localized.text: 一种健身器材用档位调节弹销结构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用公开了一种健身器材用档位调节弹销结构，本实用，包括主支架，所述主支架一端的底部活动安装有第一牛角插销，所述主支架内部两端的底部均安装有限位管，所述主支架内部两端的中间位置转动安装有伸缩支架，所述伸缩支架右侧的中间位置安装有档位板，所述伸缩支架底部安装有阻力器。本实用，设置有档位板和档位片与第一牛角插销和第二牛角插销在生产的过程中直接安装在主支架上，使健身器材在生产和运输的过程中不会产生遗漏和遗失的情况，并且能实现边生产边检验，能够准确避免调节失灵的问题，与传统的健身器材插销结构对比更稳定，受力更均匀，可以明显的增加承重能力，使用方便，可实现单手档位随时调节。

title_localized.text: Hydrochloric acid fog waste gas absorbs processing apparatus
abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to the technical field of waste gas treatment, in particular to a hydrochloric acid mist waste gas absorption treatment device, which comprises a buffer tank and a spray tower, wherein the air inlet end of the spray tower is connected with an input pipe, the air outlet end of the spray tower is connected with an exhaust part, and the air inlet end of the input pipe is connected with the air outlet end of the buffer tank through an exhaust fan; at least two groups of packing layers are arranged in the spray tower, a defogging layer is arranged on the top of an inner cavity of the spray tower, a liquid spraying pipe is arranged on the top of each group of packing layers, the bottom of the liquid spraying pipe is connected with a plurality of spray heads, and one end of the liquid spraying pipe is connected with a liquid outlet pipe; a driving rod is rotatably arranged in the spray tower; the utility model discloses well actuating lever drives spray tube and rotates around the actuating lever axis, will spray liquid and evenly spray in the packing layer, and waste gas flows through in the filler space and sprays the liquid film of liquid on the multiaspect clean shot packs and fully contacts, dissolves in aquatic, and waste gas can reach the mesh of handling hydrochloric acid fog effective absorption through the abundant contact with the liquid film of multilayer and droplet.

title_localized.text: 一种盐酸雾废气吸收处理装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及废气处理技术领域，具体公开了一种盐酸雾废气吸收处理装置，包括缓冲罐和喷淋塔，喷淋塔进气端连接输入管，喷淋塔出气端连接排气件，输入管进气端通过抽风机连接缓冲罐出气端；喷淋塔内安装至少两组填料层，喷淋塔内腔顶部安装有除雾层，每组填料层顶部均设有喷液管，喷液管底部连接有若干个喷头，喷液管一端连接出液管；喷淋塔内转动安装有驱动杆；本实用新型中驱动杆带动喷液管绕驱动杆轴线转动，将喷淋液均匀喷淋在填料层中，废气穿流于填料空隙与喷淋液在多面空心球填料上的液膜充分接触，溶于水中，废气经过与多层的液膜和雾滴的充分接触，能达到对盐酸雾有效吸收处理的目的。
inventor_harmonized.name: Wu Zhoukai

title_localized.text: Integral type bottle cleaning device
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses an integrated bottle cleaning device, wherein a base is internally provided with a first motor to a third motor which are controlled by an intermittent controller, and output shafts of the first motor to the third motor pass through the upper surface of the base; the first rotary table to the third rotary table are respectively assembled on output shafts of the first motor, the second motor and the third motor; a plurality of bottle body clamping mechanisms are uniformly arranged on the first rotary table to the third rotary table, and each bottle body clamping mechanism is respectively provided with a position sensor; a cleaning mechanism for cleaning the bottle body is arranged above the bottle body clamping mechanism corresponding to the first rotating disc, and a rotating device capable of turning over the bottle body clamping mechanism is arranged at the edge of the first rotating disc; a drying mechanism which can extend into the bottle body is arranged above the bottle body clamping mechanism corresponding to the second rotating disc; a dryer and a drying cover for drying the outside of the bottle body are arranged on the bottle body clamping mechanism corresponding to the third rotary table. The utility model discloses a clean and dry to the integration of bottle.

title_localized.text: 一种一体式瓶体清洁装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种一体式瓶体清洁装置，底座内设有由间歇控制器控制的第一电机至第三电机，第一电机至第三电机的输出轴穿过底座的上表面；第一转盘至第三转盘分别装配于第一电机、第二电机和第三电机的输出轴上；在第一转盘至第三转盘均匀设有若干瓶体夹持机构，每个瓶体夹持机构上分别设有位置传感器；对应第一转盘的瓶体夹持机构的上方设有清洗瓶体的清洁机构且第一转盘的边缘设有可将瓶体夹持机构翻转的转动装置；对应第二转盘的瓶体夹持机构的上方设有可伸入瓶体内部的干燥机构；对应第三转盘的瓶体夹持机构设有烘干瓶体外部的烘干机和烘干罩。本实用新型实现了对瓶体的一体化清洁和干燥。

title_localized.text: 改进型砂箱紧固装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种改进型砂箱紧固装置，包括C型紧固本体，C型紧固本体的底端固定安装有紧固定块，C型紧固本体的另一端安装有调节装置，调节装置的底端转动安装有紧固动块，紧固动块位于紧固定块的上方且紧固动块的紧固面与紧固定块的紧固面相对设置，调节装置带动紧固动块上下升降；紧固定块包括弧形紧固定板以及设置在弧形紧固板两侧端的水平紧固定板，紧固动块包括弧形紧固动板以及设置在弧形紧固板两侧端的水平紧固动板；本实用新型拓展了传统箱卡的使用限制，结构简单、制作成本低、使用范围广，普通铸造厂采用此种紧固装置可以完全满足生产需求，同时由于紧固方面、紧固力较强，可以有效防止产品跑火、涨箱。

title_localized.text: 一种稳定式组合连接模架
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种稳定式组合连接模架，包括支撑装置，所述支撑装置的内部底端固定安装有导向定位装置，所述支撑装置的内部两端固定安装有辅助限制装置，且所述辅助限制装置位于导向定位装置的上方，所述导向定位装置包括移动推板、齿轮、U型连接支杆、齿条和电机，所述齿轮固定安装在电机的顶端中心，所述齿条啮合在齿轮的两侧，所述U型连接支杆固定安装在齿条远离齿轮的一端顶部，所述移动推板固定安装在U型连接支杆的顶端，所述辅助限制装置包括直角移动杆、定位螺丝、支撑滑架、滑动键和气缸。本实用新型通过导向定位装置和辅助限制装置的设置，实现了可无需测量工具就可将模具稳定快速的固定在模架中心的目的。

title_localized.text: Pneumatic tool clamp
abstract_localized.text: The utility model belongs to the technical field of machining equipment, in particular to a pneumatic tool clamp which comprises a bracket, a pneumatic mechanism and a clamping mechanism; the support is of a frame structure with a rectangular frame vertical section, the pneumatic mechanism comprises an air cylinder, a reversing valve and an air cylinder throttle valve, the reversing valve is connected with the air cylinder, and the air cylinder throttle valve is arranged on an air hole of a rod cavity of the air cylinder; the clamping mechanism comprises an upper pressing plate and a lower pressing plate mechanism; the cylinder is fixedly arranged on the upper frame of the bracket, the upper pressing plate is detachably arranged at the lower end of a piston rod of the cylinder, and the lower pressing plate mechanism is fixedly arranged on the lower frame of the bracket; the utility model discloses a potential safety hazard has been avoided to the adjustability of the speed of cylinder telescopic link when pressing from both sides tightly, through the improvement of clamping mechanism, has realized the size precision to the quick accurate location of work piece, has guaranteed the sample simultaneously.

title_localized.text: 一种气动工装夹具

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型属于制砖领域，公开了一种制砖用快速固化装置，包括底座，所述底座的顶部固定连接有折板，所述折板的内部安装有冲压设备，所述底座的顶部滑动连接有两个电动推杆，两个所述电动推杆的顶端共固定连接有一个支撑板，所述支撑板上转动连接有一组转动杆，所述支撑板上设置有驱动机构，所述支撑板的底部设置有回形棉布，所述回形棉布套设至转动杆的外侧，所述回形棉布的外侧固定连接有绒毛层，所述底座的顶部分别安装有油盒与模具。该实用新型，具备良好的油液涂抹效率与效果，可减少涂抹死角存在，提升砖块生产过程中的固化成型效率。

title_localized.text: 一种防水型新能源汽车用充电桩
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及一种防水型新能源汽车用充电桩，包括充电桩本体，所述充电桩本体的顶部固定连接有挡雨板，所述充电桩本体的正面设置有充电头，所述充电桩本体的正面铰接有防护盖，所述防护盖的右侧固定连接有固定杆，所述充电桩本体上设置有限位机构，所述限位机构包括与充电桩本体正面固定连接的箱体。该防水型新能源汽车用充电桩，通过设置限位机构，使充电桩具备防护的功能，达到对充电桩本体进行防护的效果，通过设置挡雨板，对充电桩本体进行防护，通过设置防护盖，从而可以对防护盖内部的充电头进行防护，防止雨水对充电头造成影响，且可以防止雨水进入到充电插口的内部，方便了使用者的使用，增加了充电桩的实用性。

title_localized.text: 一种方便安装的汽车护杠
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及汽车保险杠技术领域的一种方便安装的汽车护杠，包括护杠和车头，所述护杠的底面和前表面均开设有凹槽，所述凹槽的内壁一端开设有螺纹槽，所述护杠远离凹槽的一侧面固定安装有螺纹插套，所述连接槽的内壁两侧均开设有卡槽，所述凸块远离卡槽的一端固定连接有位于螺纹槽内壁的压条，两个所述压条的相对面均开设有与螺纹槽纹路一致的螺旋纹，所述螺纹槽的内壁插设有与压条螺纹连接的螺栓。通过设置可以插进卡槽内部的凸块，可以使护杠和车头便于快速定位连接，同时凸块的一端通过压条连接在螺纹槽的内壁，可以使螺栓插入旋合时固定压条的位置，防止滑脱，该装置的设置可以使护杠和车头便于安装，并且提高安装时的精准度。

title_localized.text: Vacuum packaging machine for processing frozen meat
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a vacuum packaging machine is used in processing of freezing meat relates to the vacuum packaging machine field, to the vacuum packaging machine who is suitable for at present when processing the packing to meat, because it needs the workman to place wrapping bag and the inside meat of wrapping bag in one side of packagine machine in proper order, consequently leads to the problem that vacuum packaging machine's degree of automation is low, now proposes following scheme, and it is including placing the platform, the top of placing the platform is provided with the transport mechanism who is used for carrying out the transportation, one side of transport mechanism is provided with slewing mechanism, just slewing mechanism's top is rotated and is connected with the packagine machine body. This vacuum packaging machine for frozen meat processing is convenient for carry out quantitative transportation to the meat through setting up transport mechanism, has avoided artifical manual meat to put things in good order one side at the packagine machine body to increase the device's degree of automation, the slewing mechanism cooperation packagine machine body that the device one side set up is convenient for carry out vacuum packaging to the meat simultaneously.
inventor_harmonized.name: LI YONGHUA
assignee: 广东华平食品有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: GUANGDONG HUAPING FOOD CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种冷冻肉类加工用真空包装机
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种冷冻肉类加工用真空包装机，涉及真空包装机领域，针对目前在对肉类进行加工包装时所适用的真空包装机，由于其需要工人依次将包装袋以及包装袋内部的肉类放置在包装机的一侧，因此导致真空包装机的自动化程度低的问题，现提出如下方案，其包括放置台，所述放置台的顶部设置有用于进行运输的运输机构，所述运输机构的一侧设置有转动机构，且所述转动机构的顶部转动连接有包装机本体。该冷冻肉类加工用真空包装机通过设置运输机构便于对肉类进行定量运输，避免了人工手动将肉类码放在包装机本体的一侧，从而增加该装置的自动化程度，同时该装置一侧设置的转动机构配合包装机本体便于对肉类进行真空包装。

title_localized.text: Pet departure membrane coiling mechanism with mechanism of rectifying
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a pet is from shape membrane coiling mechanism with mechanism of rectifying, including linking plate and the structure of rectifying, fixedly connected with backup pad between two linking plates, fixedly connected with fixed plate in the backup pad, the inboard rotation of fixed plate is connected with first live-rollers, two first live-rollers inboards are provided with two second live-rollers, all peg graft on first live-rollers and the second live-rollers have brush and from the type membrane contact, the backup pad is close to first live-rollers one side fixedly connected with exhaust column, exhaust column one side fixedly connected with fixed frame is kept away from to the backup pad, the utility model discloses a first live-rollers rotates and clears up from the type membrane outside, and utilizes the second live-rollers to clear up from the type membrane inboard, and produces negative pressure state through guide way and air pump, pulls the dust that is close to second live-rollers department, can handle the epimembranal dust of rolling, can reduce the in-process and produce the fold, reduce skew phenomenon.
inventor_harmonized.name: LIU WENYONG
assignee: 无锡胶大电子材料有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: WUXI JIAODA ELECTRONIC MAT CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种带有纠偏机构的pet离形膜收卷装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种带有纠偏机构的pet离形膜收卷装置，包括衔接板和纠偏结构，两个衔接板之间固定连接有支撑板，支撑板内固定连接有固定板，固定板内侧转动连接有第一转动辊，两个第一转动辊内侧设置有两个第二转动辊，第一转动辊与第二转动辊上均插接有毛刷且毛刷与离型膜接触，支撑板靠近第一转动辊一侧固定连接有抽风管，支撑板远离抽风管一侧固定连接有固定框，本实用新型通过第一转动辊转动对离型膜外侧进行清理，且利用第二转动辊对离型膜内侧进行清理，且通过导向槽及气泵产生负压状态，牵引靠近第二转动辊处的灰尘，能够处理离型膜上的灰尘，能够减少收卷过程中产生皱褶，减少偏移现象。
inventor_harmonized.name: CHEN JIFENG

title_localized.text: Landscape water cyclic utilization device
abstract_localized.text: The application discloses landscape water cyclic utilization device relates to water filtration technical field, including the header tank, the inside water assembly that is provided with of header tank, the right side outer wall of header tank is fixed with the subassembly that catchments, the outer wall of subassembly that catchments has cup jointed multiunit axis of rotation, multiunit the left side outer wall of axis of rotation is fixed with first filter hopper, second filter hopper and third filter hopper respectively, the top and the bottom of first filter hopper, second filter hopper and third filter hopper all are the opening form, first filter hopper sets up directly over the second filter hopper, the second filter hopper sets up directly over the third filter hopper, the top of header tank is run through to the bottom of third filter hopper. This application staff closes the subassembly that catchments, makes the water of collecting in landscape no longer get into first filter hopper through the subassembly that catchments, makes first filter hopper and second filter hopper do circular motion around the stand through first filter hopper and second filter hopper.
inventor_harmonized.name: ZHOU WANGCHENG
assignee: 中方通建设(深圳)有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: ZHONGFANGTONG CONSTRUCTION SHENZHEN CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种园林景观水体循环利用装置
abstract_localized.text: 本申请公开了一种园林景观水体循环利用装置，涉及水体过滤技术领域，包括集水箱，所述集水箱内部设置有出水组件，所述集水箱的右侧外壁固定有集水组件，所述集水组件的外壁通过轴承套接有多组转动轴，多组所述转动轴的左侧外壁分别固定有第一过滤斗、第二过滤斗和第三过滤斗，所述第一过滤斗、第二过滤斗和第三过滤斗的顶部和底部均呈开口状，所述第一过滤斗设置在第二过滤斗的正上方，所述第二过滤斗设置在第三过滤斗的正上方，所述第三过滤斗的底部贯穿集水箱的顶部。本申请工作人员关闭集水组件，使在园林景观中收集到的水不再通过集水组件进入第一过滤斗中，通过第一过滤斗和第二过滤斗使第一过滤斗和第二过滤斗围绕立柱做圆周运动。

title_localized.text: Gate structure and thermal insulation pipeline
abstract_localized.text: The application provides a gate structure and thermal insulation pipeline relates to glass production technical field. Wherein, the gate structure includes: the two temperature insulation doors are connected in the connecting pipe in a sliding manner, extend along a first direction and are oppositely arranged along a second direction; the thermal insulation door includes: the door plates can reciprocate along a second direction relative to the connecting pipes and are used for communicating or separating the connecting pipes; the first direction and the second direction are both horizontal directions, and the second direction is perpendicular to the first direction. This application technical scheme can control the connecting pipe through the temperature door that separates that a plurality of door plant are constituteed, adjusts opening and closing of connecting pipe, and the gate door body that can solve among the prior art integral type is because the volume is great, and temperature is inhomogeneous everywhere, easy distortion, leads to the technical problem that the gate became invalid and influence production.
inventor_harmonized.name: LI QING
assignee: 河北光兴半导体技术有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: HEBEI GUANGXING SEMICONDUCTOR TECH CO LTD

title_localized.text: 闸门结构以及隔温管道
abstract_localized.text: 本申请提供一种闸门结构以及隔温管道，涉及玻璃生产技术领域。其中，闸门结构包括：两个隔温门，用于滑动连接于连接管中，两个隔温门沿第一方向延伸，且沿第二方向相对设置；隔温门包括：沿第一方向排列的多个门板，门板能够相对连接管沿第二方向往复移动，用于连通或分隔连接管；其中，第一方向和第二方向均为水平方向，且第二方向与第一方向相互垂直。本申请技术方案可以通过多个门板组成的隔温门对连接管进行控制，调节连接管的开通和关闭，能够解决现有技术中一体式的闸门门体因为体积较大，各处温度不均匀，容易扭曲变形，导致闸门失效影响生产的技术问题。
inventor_harmonized.name: LI HERAN
assignee: 北京远大信达科技有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: BEIJING YUANDA XINDA TECH CO LTD

title_localized.text: Cell culture device capable of performing classified culture
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a cell culture device of gradable cultivation relates to cell culture device technical field, and its technical scheme main points are: including the rack, the top surface of rack is provided with the standing groove, the quantity of standing groove is provided with five, the inside of standing groove is provided with the culture dish, the inner wall of standing groove is provided with the spread groove, the inner wall fixedly connected with anti-skidding card strip of spread groove, through being connected between layer board and the draw-in groove, make the utility model discloses can stack a plurality of culture dishes of tumour cell classification culture respectively in the standing groove, at the occupation space who has reduced a plurality of culture dishes, increase and the culture dish outer wall between frictional force make the culture dish be difficult for dropping in the standing groove through anti-skidding card strip, and carry out the sign record to the culture dish that the standing groove was placed through the sign board of rack top surface, avoided the multiple marking operation to the culture dish, made things convenient for the user to seek the culture dish fast.
inventor_harmonized.name: GU JUE
assignee: 南通大学附属医院
assignee_harmonized.name: AFFILIATED HOSPITAL OF NANTONG UNIV

title_localized.text: 一种可分类培养的细胞培养装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种可分类培养的细胞培养装置，涉及细胞培养装置技术领域，其技术方案要点是：包括放置架，所述放置架的顶面设置有放置槽，所述放置槽的数量设置有五个，所述放置槽的内部设置有培养皿，所述放置槽的内壁设置有连接槽，所述连接槽的内壁固定连接有防滑卡条，通过托板与卡槽之间的连接，使得本实用新型可以对肿瘤细胞分类培养的多个培养皿分别叠放在放置槽内，在减少了多个培养皿的占用空间，通过防滑卡条增加与培养皿外壁之间的摩擦力使培养皿在放置槽内不易掉落，且通过放置架顶面的标识板对放置槽内放置的培养皿进行标识记录，避免了对培养皿的多次标记操作，方便了使用者快速对培养皿进行查找。
inventor_harmonized.name: ZHANG SIMING

title_localized.text: Bearing capacity reinforced prestressed pipe pile
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a prestressing force tubular pile of bearing capacity reinforcing relates to the tubular pile field, including main concrete layer, the both ends symmetry on main concrete layer is provided with the end fixed disk, the outside limit on main concrete layer has evenly been seted up and has been run through the end hole, the outside limit of end fixed disk has evenly been seted up and has been connected the screw, one the end fixed disk has grafting end block in the one end horizontal welding of keeping away from main concrete layer, fixed screw has evenly been seted up on the outside limit of grafting end block, one the end fixed disk has the cooperation ring body in one side horizontal welding of keeping away from main concrete layer, the cooperation through-hole has evenly been seted up on the outside limit of cooperation ring body, has made mutual butt joint position stability stronger under the structure of having adopted multiple reinforcement, has increased the further stability that has increased of outside parcel formula reinforced structure simultaneously, and also have apparent promotion effect to the bearing capacity of main part, and it is stronger to make its longer solidity in life when using.
inventor_harmonized.name: XU ZHONGMING
assignee: 北海德润建材有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: BEIHAI DERUN BUILDING MAT CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种承载力增强的预应力管桩
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种承载力增强的预应力管桩，涉及管桩领域，包括主混凝体层，所述主混凝体层的两端对称设置有端固定盘，所述主混凝体层的外侧边均匀开设有贯穿端孔，所述端固定盘的外侧边均匀开设有连接螺孔，一块所述端固定盘在远离主混凝体层的一端水平焊接有插接端块，所述插接端块的外侧边均匀开设有固定螺孔，一块所述端固定盘在远离主混凝体层的一侧边水平焊接有配合环体，所述配合环体的外侧边均匀开设有配合通孔，在采用了多重的加固的结构下使得相互之间对接连接位置稳定性更强，同时增加了外部的包裹式加固结构进一步的增加了稳定性，且对主体的承载力也有着显著的提升效果，让其在使用时寿命更长坚固度更强。
inventor_harmonized.name: YANG WUYUN

title_localized.text: Drying equipment is used in production of high-efficient drier
abstract_localized.text: The utility model provides a drying equipment is used in production of high-efficient drier belongs to drier production facility technical field, and this drying equipment is used in production of high-efficient drier includes the bottom plate, top one side fixedly connected with support of bottom plate, the top of support is rotated and is connected with a jar body, one side middle part swing joint that the support was kept away from to the bottom plate has hydraulic push rod, hydraulic push rod's top is rotated with one side bottom of the jar body and is connected, the bottom fixedly connected with motor of the jar body, the inside of the jar body is rotated and is connected with the pivot, the output shaft and the pivot fixed connection of motor, the outside fixedly connected with stirring rake of pivot, top one side of the jar body is provided with the opening. This drying equipment is used in production of high-efficient drier through the cooperation between hydraulic push rod, support and the jar body, can make jar body to a lopsidedness to pour out jar internal reactant, easy operation is laborsaving, is convenient for take out jar internal reactant, and it is more convenient to use.
inventor_harmonized.name: LI JIANKUN
assignee: 郑州中岳高新材料有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: ZHENGZHOU ZHONGYUE HIGH AND NEW MAT CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种高效催干剂生产用烘干设备
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型提供一种高效催干剂生产用烘干设备，属于催干剂生产设备技术领域，该高效催干剂生产用烘干设备包括底板，所述底板的顶部一侧固定连接有支架，所述支架的顶部转动连接有罐体，所述底板远离支架的一侧中部活动连接有液压推杆，所述液压推杆的顶端与罐体的一侧底部转动连接，所述罐体的底部固定连接有电机，所述罐体的内部转动连接有转轴，所述电机的输出轴与转轴固定连接，所述转轴的外侧固定连接有搅拌桨，所述罐体的顶部一侧设置有开口。该高效催干剂生产用烘干设备，通过液压推杆、支架和罐体之间的配合，能够使罐体向一侧倾斜，从而将罐体内部的反应物倒出，操作简单省力，便于将罐体内部的反应物取出，使用更加方便。
inventor_harmonized.name: WANG HAITAO

title_localized.text: Tractor keeps off position detection mechanism and tractor
abstract_localized.text: The utility model provides a tractor keeps off position detection mechanism and tractor. Tractor keeps off position detection mechanism includes: the sensor comprises a sensor connecting rod, a shifting fork, a sensor connecting seat, a sensor toggle pin shaft and a sensor connecting support used for being connected with a sensor, wherein one end of the sensor connecting rod is connected with one end face of the shifting fork, the sensor connecting seat is installed at the other end of the sensor connecting rod, the sensor toggle pin shaft is installed on the sensor connecting seat, the sensor toggle pin shaft protrudes out of the sensor connecting seat, and one end of the sensor connecting support is clamped with the sensor toggle pin shaft. Through the design of the transmission mechanism between the shifting fork and the sensor, the sensor is convenient to be connected with the shifting fork, the sensor is convenient to detect the position of the shifting fork, the gear detection is convenient to realize, and the problem of whether the gear is hooked in place or not is convenient to solve.
inventor_harmonized.name: Hu Zunqiang
assignee: 潍柴雷沃智慧农业科技股份有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: WEICHAI LEIWO SMART AGRICULTURE TECH CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种拖拉机挡位检测机构以及拖拉机
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型提供了一种拖拉机挡位检测机构以及拖拉机。拖拉机挡位检测机构包括：传感器连接杆、拨叉、传感器连接座、传感器拨动销轴以及用于与传感器连接的传感器连接支架，所述传感器连接杆的一端与所述拨叉的一端端面连接，所述传感器连接座安装在所述传感器连接杆的另一端，所述传感器拨动销轴安装在所述传感器连接座上，所述传感器拨动销轴凸出所述传感器连接座，传感器连接支架的一端与所述传感器拨动销轴卡接。通过设计拨叉与传感器之间的传动机构，便于传感器与拨叉连接，便于传感器检测拨叉的位置，便于实现挡位检测，便于解决挡位是否挂接到位的问题。
inventor_harmonized.name: LI XUESHUN

title_localized.text: Leakage detector for air outlet of automobile air conditioner
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a leakage amount detector is let out to vehicle air conditioner air outlet, comprising a base plate, bottom plate upper surface one side is fixed with the backplate, the backplate top is fixed with test bellows, the inside baffle that is equipped with of test bellows, test bellows both sides all are connected with tuber pipe and controller, the backplate both sides all are connected with first bounding wall through the hinge rotation. The utility model discloses in, be provided with bottom plate, backplate, test bellows, two first bounding walls, two second bounding walls and baffle strip, two second bounding walls bottoms all are equipped with the block structure, baffle strip middle part is equipped with the draw-in groove, and two first bounding walls rotate with the backplate both sides to be connected, and two second bounding walls rotate with two first bounding walls respectively to be connected, consequently when this detector of production equipment, can rotate first bounding wall and second bounding wall completely and open for the space of bottom plate top is bigger, thereby gives and is convenient for at detection device such as bottom plate surface mounting gas flowmeter.
inventor_harmonized.name: SHI YUN
assignee: 苏州市丰本精密自动化设备有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: SUZHOU FENGBEN PREC AUTOMATION EQUIPMENT CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种汽车空调出风口泄漏量检测仪
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种汽车空调出风口泄漏量检测仪，包括底板，所述底板上表面一侧固定有背板，所述背板顶端固定有测试风箱，所述测试风箱内部设有隔板，所述测试风箱两侧均连接有风管和控制器，所述背板两侧均通过铰链转动连接有第一围板。本实用新型中，设置有底板、背板、测试风箱、两个第一围板、两个第二围板和挡板条，两个第二围板底部均设有卡合结构，所述挡板条中部设有卡槽，两个第一围板与背板两侧转动连接，两个第二围板分别与两个第一围板转动连接，因此在生产组装该检测仪时，可以将第一围板和第二围板完全转动打开，使得底板上方的空间更大，从而给便于在底板表面安装气体流量计等检测装置。

title_localized.text: High-precision current sampling device
abstract_localized.text: The application relates to a high-precision current sampling device, which belongs to the technical field of current sampling and comprises a sampling resistor unit and a heating unit, wherein the sampling resistor unit comprises a sampling resistor and a circuit board, and the sampling resistor is connected to the circuit board and used for sampling current; the heating unit comprises a PTC resistor, and the PTC resistor is placed below the sampling resistor and used for directly heating the sampling resistor to a preset temperature. The present application has the following effects: reduce the heat energy loss, more can heat sampling resistor to predetermined temperature accurately, reduce sampling resistor because the resistance change that the temperature drifts the cause, promoted the sampling precision, and overall design scheme simple structure, the operation of being convenient for.
inventor_harmonized.name: LIU JUN
assignee: 深圳市英可瑞数字能源技术有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: SHENZHEN YINGKERUI DIGITAL ENERGY TECH CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种高精度的电流采样装置
abstract_localized.text: 本申请涉及一种高精度的电流采样装置，属于电流采样技术领域，其包括采样电阻单元和加热单元，所述采样电阻单元包括采样电阻和电路板，所述采样电阻连接在电路板上，用于对电流采样；所述加热单元包括PTC电阻，所述PTC电阻放置在采样电阻的下方，用于将采样电阻直接加热到预设温度。本申请具有以下效果：减少热能损耗，更能精确地将采样电阻加热到预设的温度，降低采样电阻由于温漂造成的电阻变化，提升了采样精度，且整体设计方案结构简单，便于操作。
inventor_harmonized.name: LAN ZHOU

title_localized.text: Power grid parameter sampling module system
abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to a power grid parameter sampling module system, which comprises a processor, current signal sampling module, voltage signal sampling module, electric energy metering module, communication module, power module, current signal sampling module's output, voltage signal sampling module's output is connected electric energy metering module's input respectively, electric energy metering module's output connection processor's input, the treater is connected with the communication module electricity, power module is the treater respectively, current signal sampling module, voltage signal sampling module, electric energy metering module, communication module provides operating voltage. The utility model discloses electric wire netting parameter sampling module system has the manufacturing cost of convenient to use, reducible equipment and the advantage of equipment treater work load.

The utility model discloses in hydroformylation reaction process, utilize multilayer titanium alloy sintering board to press from both sides polytetrafluoroethylene filtration membrane, fine rhodium catalyst and the macromolecule ligand that has blockked passes through, guarantee that the reaction liquid through filtration membrane only is diisobutylene and the product isononanal for the reaction, guaranteed that product separation rectification in-process catalyst is not wherein, only lets the catalyst participate in the reaction stage, greatly increased the reaction life of catalyst.

title_localized.text: 一种连续法烯烃氢甲酰化反应的反应器
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种连续法烯烃氢甲酰化反应的反应器，包括壳体，所述壳体的顶部设有合成气入口，底部设有异壬醛/未反应的二异丁烯出口，一侧的上部设有二异丁烯入口、控温油出口，另一侧的下部设有控温油入口；壳体内上部设有合成气进气分布环，底部设有过滤装置。本实用新型在氢甲酰化反应过程中，利用多层钛合金烧结板夹聚四氟乙烯过滤膜，很好的阻挡了铑催化剂及大分子配体通过，保证通过过滤膜的反应液只有为反应的二异丁烯和产品异壬醛，保证了产品分离精馏过程中催化剂不在其中，只让催化剂参与反应阶段，大大增加了催化剂的反应寿命。

title_localized.text: 一种尼龙管道加工用除尘装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型提供的一种尼龙管道加工用除尘装置，涉及除尘技术领域,包括：底座，所述底座的顶部固定插设有一组金属杆，一组所述金属杆的外表壁之间固定套设有防护外壳。首先把要清理的尼龙管插入刷子主体中，通过启动电动伸缩杆，这样就可以把尼龙管固定在装置上，这时启动第一电机，就带动了尼龙管向前移动，然后启动第二电机，会使得刷子主体进行旋转，由于刷子是由内外两个刷子组成的，所以当尼龙管向前推进时，内外两个刷子就会对尼龙管的内表壁和外表壁的浆液进行清理，这样一来，就解决了现有技术中尼龙管由人工进行表面除尘工作，而无法对尼龙管内部进行除尘，导致尼龙管道在加工时费时费力的问题。

title_localized.text: Catch for cabinet door
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a touching clamp for cabinet door which comprises a clamp body and a touching block which are respectively arranged on the cabinet door and the cabinet wall. A guide post, a guide post cavity, a guide post hole, and a guide post restoring spring are arranged in the clamp body. When the cabinet door is closed or opened, either of the crossed inclined planes arranged under the guide post is given the upward pushing force, so the guide post can do the upward movement, and then the guide post can do the downward movement under the action of the restoring spring. The guide post and the touching block can be reliably positioned through the reciprocating movement of the guide post, and the cabinet door can be tightly closed without preventing the convenient open of the cabinet door.

title_localized.text: 一种引水渠导向结构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型属于农业水利技术领域，尤其为一种引水渠导向结构，包括主体，所述主体的上端设有防护板，所述防护板的下端设有土层板，所述土层板的下端设有过滤板，所述过滤板的内部开设有分置槽，所述分置槽的内部设有沙层板，通过防护板的W形设置，从而达到将树叶等各种较大的杂物进行有效的阻挡，同时便于对雨水进行有效的收集；当水经过土层板时经过第一次过滤，向下渗漏，进入过滤板与沙层板的内部进行有效的沉淀与二次过滤，进入活性炭板的内部进行有效的净化；通过土层板、过滤板与活性炭板的设置，有效对水进行过滤与沉淀的；同时通过土层板、过滤板与活性炭板对阳光进行有效的阻挡，避免水大量蒸发，便于水的储存。

title_localized.text: Roadbed slope protection structure
abstract_localized.text: The application discloses a roadbed slope protection structure, which comprises a plurality of protection components in a rectangular array on a roadbed slope, wherein each protection component comprises two protection units; the protection unit comprises a first baffle, a second baffle, a third baffle and a water channel bottom plate, wherein the first baffle, the second baffle and the third baffle are sequentially connected into a triangular structure, and the first baffle is vertical to the second baffle; in each protection assembly, two third baffles are attached; the first baffle is arranged along the width of the roadbed side slope, and the bottom of the first baffle is provided with a drainage channel; the second baffle is arranged along the length of the roadbed slope, the bottom of the second baffle is provided with a communicating groove, and the communicating grooves in the adjacent second baffles in the width direction of the roadbed slope are communicated; the water channel bottom plate is connected to the bottom of the first baffle plate, and the adjacent water channel bottom plates in the length direction of the roadbed slope are spliced. This application can be with the rainwater discharge on the side slope of road bed, and then prevented that the road bed is not hard up, guaranteed the stability of road bed and side slope of road bed.

abstract_localized.text: 本申请公开了一种路基边坡防护结构，该路基边坡防护结构包括在路基边坡上呈矩形阵列的多个防护组件，防护组件包括两个防护单元；防护单元包括第一挡板、第二挡板、第三挡板和水道底板，第一挡板、第二挡板和第三挡板依次连接成三角型结构，且第一挡板和第二挡板垂直；在每个防护组件中，两个第三挡板贴合；第一挡板沿路基边坡宽度设置，第一挡板的底部开设有排水槽；第二挡板沿路基边坡长度设置，第二挡板的底部开设有连通槽，在路基边坡的宽度方向的相邻第二挡板上的连通槽贯通；水道底板连接于第一挡板的底部，在路基边坡长度方向相邻的水道底板拼接。本申请能够将路基边坡上的雨水排出，进而防止了路基松动，保证了路基及路基边坡的稳定性。

title_localized.text: Head, dental handpiece and root canal preparation machine
abstract_localized.text: The utility model provides a aircraft nose, dental handpiece and root canal preparation machine relates to dental medical instrument technical field. The handpiece is applied to the dental handpiece and comprises a movement and a driving mechanism for driving the movement to rotate; the outer side wall of the machine core is provided with a closed guide groove, and the driving mechanism is provided with a contact head which is contacted with the guide groove; the contact head and the guide groove form a cylindrical cam mechanism, wherein the contact head is used for applying acting force to the inner wall of the guide groove when the movement rotates, so that the movement does reciprocating linear motion in the direction parallel to the axial direction of the movement. When the root canal is enlarged, the dental handpiece does not need to be moved manually to adjust the depth of the file needle in the root canal, so that the treatment efficiency of the root canal enlargement can be effectively improved, and the difficulty of the root canal enlargement treatment is reduced.

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种中空的保温挤塑板，其技术方案是：包括基板，所述基板包括外板和内板，所述外板和内板通过第一胶层粘接，所述外板靠近内板一侧设置有多个均匀分布的槽腔，所述基板两侧均设置有加强板，所述外板通过第二胶层与加强板粘接，所述内板通过第三胶层与加强板粘接，所述加强板设置为铝板，所述加强板靠近基板一侧设置有多个均匀分布的弧面凸起，一种中空的保温挤塑板有益效果是：通过在基板两侧设置加强板可提高板材表面的抗压强度，避免局部应力过大造成表面损坏开裂，同时通过在基板内部设置槽腔，在保证抗压强度的同时控制合适的重量，节省了材料成本，方便了安装工作。

title_localized.text: Self-adaptive transport cabin
abstract_localized.text: The utility model provides a self-adaptive transport cabin, which comprises a carrying chassis, a square cabin and an auxiliary frame; the auxiliary frame is arranged on the carrying chassis, and the square cabin and the carrying chassis are quickly connected and separated through the auxiliary frame; electric support legs for lifting the square cabin are arranged on two sides of the square cabin; the auxiliary frame comprises square steel, an automatic alignment mechanism, an electric rotating lock and corner pieces, the frame of the auxiliary frame is formed by the square steel and the corner pieces, the electric rotating lock used for locking the square cabin is installed on the corner pieces, the automatic alignment mechanism is installed on a middle cross beam of the frame, and the automatic alignment mechanism is matched with an alignment structure arranged at the bottom of the square cabin, so that the square cabin can be accurately positioned with the auxiliary frame in the falling process. The utility model discloses a transport cabin can make shelter and delivery chassis location accurate through automatic alignment mechanism to carry out high-speed joint or separation through electronic twist lock.

title_localized.text: 一种自适应运输舱

abstract_localized.text: The utility model provides an agricultural non-point source pollution runoff monitoring devices relates to agricultural non-point source pollution monitoring devices technical field, including the monitoring case, the one end lower part fixed mounting of monitoring case has a drainage section of thick bamboo, and the inside one end fixed mounting of monitoring case has the protection box, and the inside of protection box has been seted up perpendicular groove, and the intake chamber has been seted up to the both sides of protection box, and the inside movable mounting of protection box has floating level sensor, and floating level sensor's both ends fixed mounting has the connecting block, and the inboard of connecting block is provided with the pivot, and the connecting block has the gyro wheel through pivot swing joint, and the mounting hole has been seted up on the inboard upper portion of monitoring case. The utility model discloses the gyro wheel of well floating level sensor both sides and the inboard laminating of erecting the groove make the vertical shifting up of floating level sensor, and floating level sensor can monitor the runoff, can shunt the water through the flow distribution plate, can effectually protect the inside floating level sensor of protection box, makes monitoring data more accurate.

title_localized.text: 一种农业面源污染径流监测装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型提供一种农业面源污染径流监测装置，涉及农业面源污染监测装置技术领域，包括监测箱，监测箱的一端下部固定安装有引流筒，监测箱的内部一端固定安装有保护盒，保护盒的内部开设有竖槽，保护盒的两侧开设有进水槽，保护盒的内部活动安装有浮式水位传感器，浮式水位传感器的两端固定安装有连接块，连接块的内侧设置有转轴，连接块通过转轴活动连接有滚轮，监测箱的内侧上部开设有安装孔。本实用新型中浮式水位传感器两侧的滚轮和竖槽的内侧贴合，使浮式水位传感器竖直上移，浮式水位传感器可以对径流进行监测，通过分流板可以将水分流，能够有效的对保护盒内部的浮式水位传感器进行保护，使监测数据更为准确。

title_localized.text: 一种薯类原料检测设备
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型提供一种薯类原料检测设备，包括检测设备的主体，所述主体的一侧设置有操作区，对应所述操作区在主体上设置有用以对其进行遮罩的遮盖机构，所述主体的下部设置有检测插针，所述检测插针两侧且在主体的下部设置有用以对其进行防护的防护机构，可以通过与检测插针相连的防护机构对检测插针进行遮挡防护，有效避免其不慎脱落造成损坏或带来危险，同时能够在不进行使用时将操作面板进行遮挡避免误触或损坏显示屏。

abstract_localized.text: The utility model belongs to the technical field of the withstand voltage of ammeter detects, concretely relates to withstand voltage detection device of ammeter, including ammeter group, withstand voltage detector group and two backup pads, be equipped with drive mechanism between two backup pads, front side backup pad upper end is installed the detection case, withstand voltage detector group installs inside the detection case, inside fixedly connected with insulation board of detection case, be connected with the line of conduction between the detection link connection of withstand voltage detector and the through-hole, L shape conductive pillar is all installed to a plurality of mounting inslots, inside the detection case is close to drive mechanism one side fixed connection baffle, the baffle is close to drive mechanism one side fixedly connected with a plurality of springs, a plurality of springs are fixed connection jointly and are with the push pedal that matches with ammeter group, baffle lower extreme fixedly connected with insulating curtain, the cylinder is installed to the mounting panel rear end, the output of cylinder runs through mounting panel fixedly connected with ammeter group assorted roof; the utility model discloses can carry out automated inspection to the ammeter, reduce workman's tired degree.

title_localized.text: 一种电表耐压检测装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型属于电表耐压检测技术领域，具体涉及一种电表耐压检测装置，包括电表组、耐压检测仪组和两个支撑板，两个支撑板之间设有传动机构，前侧支撑板上端安装有检测箱，耐压检测仪组安装于检测箱内部，检测箱内部固定连接有绝缘板，耐压检测仪的检测连接端连接与通孔之间连接有传导线，若干安装槽内部均安装有L形导电柱，检测箱内部靠近传动机构一侧固定连接挡板，挡板靠近传动机构一侧固定连接有若干弹簧，若干弹簧共同固定连接有与电表组相匹配的推板，挡板下端固定连接有绝缘帘，安装板后端安装有气缸，气缸的输出端贯穿安装板固定连接有电表组相匹配的顶板；本实用新型能够对电表进行自动检测，减少工人的劳累程度。
inventor_harmonized.name: ZHANG BAO

title_localized.text: Magnetic roller conductive structure
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a magnetic roll conducting structure, including the magnetic sleeve that is used for installing the magnetic core, the one end of magnetic sleeve is equipped with conductive head, conductive head adopts conducting material to make, conductive head's the inner be used for laminating mutually with the inner wall of magnetic sleeve, conductive head's outside be used for with the conducting strip laminating of the electrically conductive end cover of selenium drum, conductive overhead loop type isolation portion that is equipped with, loop type isolation portion's outer lane diameter is greater than the outer lane diameter of magnetic sleeve, the terminal surface of loop type isolation portion laminates mutually with the terminal surface of magnetic sleeve, inner and the interference of magnetic sleeve are pegged graft and are cooperated. The utility model discloses an adopt conductive head that conducting material made to be connected with the magnetic sleeve, cancel the use of conducting wire to avoid current conducting wire to have the possibility of deformation in transportation or equipment process, not only make things convenient for the equipment but also can effectual improvement use quality. And simultaneously, the utility model discloses a terminal surface of loop type isolation portion laminates with the terminal surface of magnetic sleeve mutually, can solve to have the gap among the prior art and lead to the carbon dust to pile up the problem that makes the isolation cover produce deformation.

title_localized.text: 一种磁辊导电结构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开一种磁辊导电结构，包括用于安装磁芯的磁套，磁套的一端设有导电头，导电头采用导电材料制成，导电头的内端用于与磁套的内壁互相贴合，导电头的外部用于与硒鼓导电端盖的导电片贴合，导电头上设有环型隔离部，环型隔离部的外圈直径大于磁套的外圈直径，环型隔离部的端面与磁套的端面相贴合，内端与磁套过盈插接配合。本实用新型通过采用导电材料制成的导电头与磁套进行连接，取消导电丝的使用，以避免现有导电丝在运输或组装过程中存在形变的可能性，不仅方便组装而且能有效的提高使用品质。同时，本实用新型通过环型隔离部的端面与磁套的端面相贴合，能解决现有技术中存在缝隙而导致碳粉堆积使隔离套产生形变的问题。
inventor_harmonized.name: HUANG JINBO

title_localized.text: High-capacity capacitor with breakdown-preventing structure
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a large-capacity capacitor with breakdown-preventing structure, which relates to the related technical field of capacitor protection, and comprises a protective shell, wherein the top of the protective shell is provided with a limit groove, and one side of the protective shell is provided with a shielding piece, so that the shielding piece rotates clockwise to the inside of the limit groove and is in interference fit with the limit groove; the capacitor main body is placed inside the protective shell, and an electrode strip is fixedly installed at the bottom of the capacitor main body; the utility model discloses utilize the setting of spacing apron to compress tightly the condenser main part downwards to make the condenser main part pass through the power that steps up that L type layer board drove the stripper plate with the condenser main part, make condenser main part and L type layer board can't descend in the restriction of stripper plate, can't rise under spacing apron spacing, avoid the condenser main part to beat from top to bottom in transport or transportation.

title_localized.text: 大容量具备防击穿结构的电容器
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种大容量具备防击穿结构的电容器，涉及到电容器防护相关技术领域，该大容量具备防击穿结构的电容器，包括防护壳，所述防护壳的顶部开设有限位槽，所在防护壳的一侧安装有遮挡件，形成遮挡件顺时针旋转到限位槽的内部并与限位槽过盈配合；电容器主体，所述电容器主体放置在防护壳的内部，所述电容器主体的底部固定安装有电极条；本实用新型利用限位盖板的设置将电容器主体向下压紧，并使电容器主体通过L型托板带动挤压板将电容器主体的加紧力，使电容器主体和L型托板在挤压板的限制无法下降，在限位盖板的限位下无法上升，避免电容器主体在搬运或运输过程中上下跳动。

title_localized.text: Switch with a switch body
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a switch belongs to the electrical technology field. In the switch, the movable contact component comprises an elastic sheet, a wiring terminal connected to the middle part of the elastic sheet and a movable contact connected to the end part of the elastic sheet; the movable contact assembly and the fixed contact assembly are positioned in the base, and the movable contact corresponds to the fixed contact of the fixed contact assembly; the panel can be pressed and rotated relative to the base, and the transition assembly is connected to the panel and hinged to the base; the transition assembly comprises a driving rib, and the transition assembly can be pressed by the panel to act on the elastic sheet through the driving rib to enable the elastic sheet to deform, so that the movable contact is in contact with or separated from the static contact; the two opposite sides of the transition assembly are respectively provided with a through hole, the elastic positioning piece penetrates through the through holes, and two ends of the elastic positioning piece are respectively abutted against the base, so that one of the two elastic positioning pieces positioned on the two sides of the transition assembly is extruded into a concave shape, and the other elastic positioning piece is extruded into a convex shape. The switch has excellent dialing performance and hand feeling, can be ultra-thin, and has stronger dialing stability and reliability of the elastic positioning piece.
inventor_harmonized.name: CAI YINGFENG
assignee: 宁波公牛电器有限公司

title_localized.text: 开关
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了开关，属于电气技术领域。该开关中，动触点组件包括弹片、连接于弹片中部的接线端子、连接于弹片端部的动触点；动触点组件和静触点组件均位于底座内部，且动触点与静触点组件的静触点对应；面板相对于底座可按压转动，过渡组件连接于面板且铰接于底座；过渡组件包括驱动筋，过渡组件能够被面板按压以通过驱动筋作用于弹片使其变形，使得动触点与静触点接触或分离；过渡组件相对的两侧各自具有过孔，弹性定位件贯穿过孔且弹性定位件的两端分别抵接于底座，使得位于过渡组件两侧的两个弹性定位件中的一个被挤压成凹状，另一个被挤压成凸状。该开关具有优异的拨打性能和手感，能够超薄化，且弹性定位件的拨打稳定性和可靠性更强。

title_localized.text: 一种基于金属箔膜刻制的发热片
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及发热片技术领域，具体为一种基于金属箔膜刻制的发热片，所述发热片本体从上到下依次设有粘合剂层、发热体层以及承载基层，所述粘合剂层、发热体层以及承载基层依次通过粘接胶固定，所述发热体层上设有热源电路、热源区块以及刻除区块，本结构通过设有的粘合剂层、发热体层以及承载基层，能够实现，各类异形产品的发热需求，降低了发热片本体在使用时的局限性，通过设有的限位装置，能使粘合剂层、发热体层以及承载基层对接的更加牢固，提高了发热片本体在使用时的局限性。

title_localized.text: Intelligent faucet display screen assembly disinfects
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses an intelligent tap display screen subassembly disinfects, include: the shell is provided with a groove; a plurality of through holes penetrate through the groove; a PCB circuit board inserted into the groove; the PCB is electrically connected with and fixed with a plurality of LED lamps, and the LED lamps are inserted into the through holes in a matching manner; the display mirror is attached to one side of the shell; the AB glue is filled between the display mirror surface and the shell, fills a gap between the PCB circuit board and the groove by the AB glue, and covers the PCB circuit board to seal the other side of the shell; the ultraviolet sterilizing lamp is electrically connected with the PCB through a wire, and the wire extends out of the AB glue and is electrically connected with the ultraviolet sterilizing lamp. The utility model discloses have good waterproof nature and the function of disinfecting.

title_localized.text: 一种杀菌智能水龙头显示屏组件
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种杀菌智能水龙头显示屏组件，包括：外壳，所述外壳设有凹槽；所述凹槽内贯穿有多个通孔；PCB电路板，所述PCB电路板插入到所述凹槽内；所述PCB电路板上电连接并固定有多颗LED灯，所述LED灯匹配地插入到所述通孔内；显示镜面，所述显示镜面贴在所述外壳的一侧；AB胶，所述AB胶填充在显示镜面与外壳之间，以及所述AB胶将PCB电路板与凹槽之间的空隙填满，并覆盖所述PCB电路板来封闭所述外壳的另一侧；紫外杀菌灯，所述紫外杀菌灯通过导线与所述PCB电路板电连接，所述导线延伸出AB胶外与所述紫外杀菌灯电连接。本实用新型具有良好的防水性和杀菌功能。
inventor_harmonized.name: LIN CHUNFEN

title_localized.text: Emergence period weed removing device for high-yield corn cultivation
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a weeds clearing device of high yield maize cultivation's emergence period relates to weeds and clears away technical field. The utility model comprises a mounting rack, a first hydraulic cylinder and a cutting piece; the cutting piece is fixedly connected with the mounting frame through a first hydraulic cylinder; the filter plate divides the ventilation chamber into a placing chamber and a processing chamber; the active carbon plate and the spice box are sequentially placed in the placing cavity; the bottom of the storage chamber is provided with an opening, and a sliding plate is matched with the storage chamber in a sliding way; the stop lever is matched with a sliding part in a sliding way; a second hydraulic cylinder is fixedly connected between the sliding piece and the filter plate. The utility model starts the suction fan, the ventilation pipe sucks pungent odor into the processing chamber, the filtering plate enters the placing chamber, and the pungent odor of weeds is effectively processed through the activated carbon plate and the spice box; weeds are intercepted by the gear rods of each group, the controller controls the second hydraulic cylinder to do periodic telescopic motion, the L-shaped plate is driven to do periodic reciprocating motion, and the weeds wound on the gear rods are pushed into the storage chamber to be collected.
inventor_harmonized.name: IKM REBIGURI
assignee: 热比古丽·艾克木

title_localized.text: 一种高产玉米栽培的出苗期杂草清除装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种高产玉米栽培的出苗期杂草清除装置，涉及杂草清除技术领域。本实用新型包括安装架、第一液压缸和切割件；切割件与安装架通过第一液压缸固定连接；过滤板将通风室分隔为放置腔和处理腔；放置腔内部依次放置有活性炭板和香料盒；存放室底部为开口设置，且其滑动配合有滑板；档杆滑动配合有滑动件；滑动件与过滤板之间固定连接有第二液压缸。本实用新型通过启动吸风扇，通风管将刺激性气味被吸进处理腔，通过过滤板进入放置腔中，通过活性炭板和香料盒，对杂草的刺鼻气味进行有效处理；杂草被各组档杆拦截，控制器控制第二液压缸做周期性伸缩运动，带动L形板做周期性往返运动，将缠绕在档杆上的杂草推进存放室中收集。

title_localized.text: 一种用于葡萄种植的栽培架
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型属于葡萄种植领域，具体为一种用于葡萄种植的栽培架，包括展架，还包括固定串联机构和升降机构，所述固定串联机构上方设置有所述升降机构，所述升降机构顶部设置有所述展架；所述固定串联机构包括连接板、入地钉、连接架、固定销钉，所述升降机构下方并位于两侧设置有所述连接板，所述连接板下方设置有两个所述入地钉，所述连接板上方设置有所述连接架，所述连接架下方并位于两侧均设置有两个所述固定销钉，利用连接架和固定销钉来串联本装置，利用升降机构便于调节本装置，利用展架固定葡萄藤，便于依据葡萄生长高度从而灵活调节高度，有利于葡萄藤生长和挂果。

title_localized.text: Water spraying cooling device for cooked wet noodle processing process
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a cooked wet noodle course of working trickle cooling device relates to food processing technology field. The utility model discloses a waterproof frame, elasticity carding plate and cistern, waterproof frame one end is run through the joint and is had the conveyer belt, and waterproof frame bottom joint has the weighing subassembly, and waterproof frame front side is provided with the control assembly, and control assembly upper end joint is fixed with audible-visual annunciator, and waterproof inboard one end joint of frame has elasticity carding plate, and elasticity carding plate upper end joint has drive assembly, and waterproof frame bottom side central authorities are provided with the cistern, and the cistern one end is run through the joint and has the water pump. abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了环保型板材加工设备技术领域的一种环保型板材机柜的翻转切割装置，包括箱体、支撑板、门体、第一电动滑轨、第一电动滑块安装箱、除尘器和控制面板，所述支撑板固定连接在所述箱体的内腔左右侧壁之间下侧，所述门体铰接在所述箱体的前侧壁，所述第一电动滑轨固定连接在所述箱体的内腔左右侧壁上侧，所述第一电动滑块位于所述第一电动滑轨的内侧，该环保型板材机柜的翻转切割装置，结构设计合理，实现了切割装置自动清洁，降低了操作人员内的工作负担，避免了激光切割装置使用时，会产生大量的烟尘，影响工人身体健康，以及污染整个工作环境，有利于保护工人健康以及整个工作环境。

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及传动轴加工技术领域，尤其为一种传动轴加工用工装夹具，包括底板，所述底板上表面一侧固定安装有尾座，所述底板上表面另一侧固定安装有CNC电脑数控分度盘，所述尾座一侧表面和CNC电脑数控分度盘一侧表面均固定安装有L板，所述L板设置有两个，两个所述L板之间固定连接有桥板，所述桥板上表面两侧均固定安装有限位柱，所述限位柱一侧固定设有第二杠杆油缸，所述第二杠杆油缸的杠杆上端固定连接有浮动压板，本实用新型中，通过设置的V形压块和压板，能够同时对多个传动轴进行定位固定，同时，无需对传动轴两端同时进行夹持，有效扩大加工面积，避免对加工头进行遮挡。

abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses an injection mold based on internal thread injection molding is used, comprising a base plate, the last fixed surface of bottom plate is connected with two risers, two the common fixedly connected with roof of the upper surface of riser, the last fixed surface of roof is connected with the motor, the last fixed surface of roof inlays and has two bearings, every the equal fixedly connected with threaded rod of inner circle of bearing, every the first belt pulley of the equal fixedly connected with in top of threaded rod, the output fixedly connected with second belt pulley of motor. title_localized.text: 一种基于内螺纹注塑件用的注塑模具
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种基于内螺纹注塑件用的注塑模具，包括底板，所述底板的上表面固定连接有两个立板，两个所述立板的上表面共同固定连接有顶板，所述顶板的上表面固定连接有电机，所述顶板的上表面固定镶嵌有两个轴承，每个所述轴承的内圈均固定连接有螺纹杆，每个所述螺纹杆的顶端均固定连接有第一皮带轮，所述电机的输出端固定连接有第二皮带轮。该基于内螺纹注塑件用的注塑模具，通过设置的稳固块与稳固块的配合，可以使上模具移动时更加牢固，同时可以对其移动进行限位，通过设置的加固块与卡槽板的配合，利用加固块和卡槽板之间的连接，可以使上模具与下模具之间进行紧密的对接，以免对注塑件的质量造成影响。

abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to an unmanned aerial vehicle storehouse platform elevating gear, the on-line screen storage device comprises a base, the top fixed mounting of base has servo motor, the first gear of fixedly connected with on servo motor's the output shaft, the outside meshing of first gear has the second gear, the inside fixedly connected with screw thread pivot of second gear, the outside threaded connection of screw thread pivot has the screw thread cover shell, the top fixedly connected with lifter plate of screw thread cover shell, the top fixedly connected with dead lever of lifter plate, the outside sliding connection of dead lever has the backup pad, the top fixedly connected with blotter of backup pad. This unmanned aerial vehicle storehouse platform elevating gear makes the lifter plate go up and down to remove through starting servo motor and adjusts, and the screw easily strikes easily and easily leads to unmanned aerial vehicle to damage in the backup pad when avoiding unmanned aerial vehicle to descend, absorbs the impact force through blotter and buffer spring cooperation, avoids its collision in the twinkling of an eye or that lasts to cause the damage to it.

title_localized.text: 一种无人机库平台升降装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及一种无人机库平台升降装置，包括底座，所述底座的顶部固定安装有伺服电机，所述伺服电机的输出轴上固定连接有第一齿轮，所述第一齿轮的外部啮合有第二齿轮，所述第二齿轮的内部固定连接有螺纹转轴，所述螺纹转轴的外部螺纹连接有螺纹套壳，所述螺纹套壳的顶部固定连接有升降板，所述升降板的顶部固定连接有固定杆，所述固定杆的外部滑动连接有支撑板，所述支撑板的顶部固定连接有缓冲垫。该无人机库平台升降装置，通过启动伺服电机使升降板进行升降移动调节，避免无人机降落时螺旋桨容易撞击到支撑板上易导致无人机损坏，通过缓冲垫与缓冲弹簧配合吸收冲击力，避免其瞬间或持续的碰撞对其造成损伤。

title_localized.text: 一种无轨道式档案密集架储存装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种无轨道式档案密集架储存装置，涉及档案储存技术领域，包括箱体、传动箱和密封板，所述传动箱的左侧面与箱体的内侧壁固定连接，传动箱的内部设有两个螺纹丝杆，传动箱的右侧面固定镶嵌有两个第一轴承。本实用新型通过调节板的横向平移调节，配合两个定位板，能够带动密封板与箱体分离，通过密封板与箱体的分离，能够将储存机构从箱体内部向外伸出，通过储存机构的伸出，起到放置档案的目的，通过螺纹丝杆的反向转动，能够使调节板往回调节，便于带动储存机构收缩进箱体内部，达到对档案进行储存的目的，该方式在使用过程中无需采用轨道，解决采用抽拉方式，增加了档案取放过程中的稳定性。

title_localized.text: Container with ventilation mechanism
abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to a container technical field especially relates to a container with ventilation mechanism. The technical scheme comprises the following steps: container body, baffle, ventilation pipe, electric putter and connecting block, the ventilation pipe is installed in the embedding of container body one side outer wall, first cutting ferrule is installed to ventilation pipe inner wall one side, electric putter is installed in the inside rotation of first cutting ferrule, ventilation pipe one end outer wall is provided with the baffle, the baffle deviates from ventilation pipe one side outer wall and installs the connecting block, the second cutting ferrule is installed to baffle one side outer wall, the rotation of electric putter one end inside and outside wall is installed inside the second cutting ferrule, through setting up ventilation pipe, electric putter and baffle, has reached the effect that the security was deposited to the improvement goods, when guaranteeing that the container body is external to be linked together, can reach the purpose of separation container body and outside air circulation, avoids the inside article of container body to receive humid air's influence, has guaranteed depositing the security of article.

title_localized.text: 一种具有通风机构的集装箱
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及集装箱技术领域，尤其涉及一种具有通风机构的集装箱。其技术方案包括：集装箱本体、挡板、通风管、电动推杆和连接块，所述集装箱本体一侧外壁嵌入安装有通风管，所述通风管内壁一侧安装有第一卡套，所述第一卡套内部转动安装有电动推杆，所述通风管一端外壁设置有挡板，所述挡板背离通风管一侧外壁安装有连接块，所述挡板一侧外壁安装有第二卡套，所述电动推杆一端内外壁转动安装于第二卡套内部，通过设置通风管、电动推杆和挡板，达到了提高货物存放安全性的效果，保证集装箱本体外界相连通的同时，能够达到了阻隔集装箱本体与外界空气流通的目的，避免集装箱本体内部的物件受到潮湿空气的影响，保证了物件的存放安全性。

title_localized.text: Inner barrel structure of dustbin
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses an inner barrel structure of a dustbin; the garbage can comprises a garbage can outer frame, wherein an inner barrel is arranged inside the garbage can outer frame, the inner barrel comprises a first panel, a filtering panel, a liquid storage frame and a second panel, and the first panel and the second panel are respectively provided with two blocks which are mutually clamped together; the filtering panel and the liquid storage frame are fixed at the bottoms of the first panel and the second panel through a fastening assembly consisting of supporting legs and fastening screws; divide into by first panel, filter panel, second panel and hold the liquid frame and constitute interior bucket through the interior bucket with original overall structure, can come with its quick split when the cleaning and disinfection of follow-up, make original overall structure become a plurality of individual structures, thereby the convenience carries out thorough cleaning and disinfection to solitary individual, all expose each face, the abluent region has been enlarged, thereby avoid the appearance at clean dead angle, realize better cleaning and disinfection effect.

title_localized.text: 一种垃圾箱的内桶结构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种垃圾箱的内桶结构；涉及垃圾箱技术领域，具体包括垃圾箱外框，该垃圾箱外框的内部设置有内桶，所述内桶由包括第一面板、过滤面板、蓄液框以及第二面板组成，所述第一面板以及第二面板各有两块且相互卡接在一起；所述过滤面板以及蓄液框通过由支撑脚和紧固螺杆组成的紧固组件固定在第一面板与第二面板的底部；通过将原有整体结构的内桶分为由第一面板、过滤面板、第二面板以及蓄液框组成内桶，能够在后续的清洗消毒时能够将其快速的拆分开来，使原有的整体结构变为多个个体的结构，从而方便对单独的个体进行彻底的清洗消毒，将各个面都暴露出来，扩大了清洗的区域，从而避免清洁死角的出现，实现更好的清洁消毒效果。
inventor_harmonized.name: JU JING

title_localized.text: Feeding mechanism of bagged spring gluing machine
abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to a feeding mechanism of spring viscose machine in bags, its characterized in that: the welding cutting device comprises a channel changing feeding mechanism, a welding cutting mechanism and a belt conveying mechanism which are arranged in sequence; the lane changing and feeding mechanism comprises a lane changing base and a feeding mechanism which is slidably arranged on the lane changing base; the feeding mechanism comprises a plurality of groups of feeding channels; the welding cut-off mechanism is arranged between the lane changing feeding mechanism and the belt conveying mechanism; the belt conveying mechanism comprises two groups of conveying belts arranged in parallel, a clamping spring mechanism and a width adjusting mechanism; one end of each of the two groups of conveying belts is connected with a second driving motor for driving the conveying belts to run. The utility model draws a plurality of groups of bagged spring strips with different specifications of the feeding channels into the belt conveying mechanism through a group of movable spring clamping mechanisms, and the bagged spring strips are continuously conveyed into the gluing machine by the belt conveying mechanism; and the feeding baffle is arranged on the feeding channel, so that the bagged spring strip can be prevented from backing up, and the influence on normal feeding is avoided.
inventor_harmonized.name: DU YONGQIN
assignee: 广东昱纶智能科技有限公司
assignee_harmonized.name: GUANGDONG YULUN INTELLIGENT TECH CO LTD

title_localized.text: 一种袋装弹簧粘胶机的送料机构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及一种袋装弹簧粘胶机的送料机构，其特征在于：包括依次排列设置的换道进料机构、焊接切断机构和皮带输送机构；所述换道进料机构包括换道底座和可滑动地安装在该换道底座上的进料机构；所述进料机构包括若干组进料通道；所述焊接切断机构设在所述换道进料机构与皮带输送机构之间；所述皮带输送机构包括两组平行设置的输送皮带、夹簧机构和宽度调节机构；两组所述输送皮带的一端连接有驱动其运行的第二驱动电机。本实用新型通过一组可移动的夹簧机构将多组进料通道不同规格的袋装弹簧条拉到皮带输送机构中，由皮带输送机构将袋装弹簧条继续输送至粘胶机内；并且进料通道上设置有进料挡板，能够防止袋装弹簧条倒退，避免影响正常进料。

title_localized.text: 一种单色胶印机
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开一种单色胶印机，包括胶印机本体和载料板，胶印机本体上方侧位上开设有入纸口，入纸口两侧外壁上均固定安装有侧位挡纸板，入纸口下方侧壁上固定安装有载料板，载料板两侧外壁上均固定安装有侧位延展板，载料板远离入纸口一侧外壁上固定安装有后延展板，两个侧位延展板外表面中心位置均固定安装有伺服气缸，伺服气缸的输出端活动连接有气缸输出杆，气缸输出杆顶端固定安装有规整板，本实用新型当工人在放置纸张时可放置在载料板的任意位置，无需人工进行反复确认，增加工作效率，通过伺服气缸和规整板组成的规整机构，可对纸张进行规整，使其处于入料的中间位置，降低纸张入料时的误差和偏差，增加胶印机的入纸质量。

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种便于上下料的切膜机，包括切膜机和卷膜筒，所述切膜机的进料口一侧设有底座，所述底座的两侧均设于挡板，两个所述挡板的相向面均活动设有一组连接块，每组所述连接块的末端均滑动连接有接头，所述接头朝向挡板的端面设有弹簧，所述卷膜筒的两侧均开设有插槽。本实用新型通过卷膜筒一侧的插槽对接接头后，再推动卷膜筒顶动接头向挡板位移，使卷膜筒的另一端与另一个接头对接时存在一定距离，最后通过放松卷膜筒，使弹簧将顶动接头向松卷膜筒位移，从而使卷膜筒的另一端与另一个接头对接，方便了安装卷膜筒。

title_localized.text: 一种便于安装的预制装配式钢筋混凝土盖板涵洞
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种便于安装的预制装配式钢筋混凝土盖板涵洞，涉及公路工程技术领域。本实用新型包括U型框，U型框的两侧内壁底部均设置有卡槽，卡槽的内部设置有扩张组件，扩张组件包括压板和密封垫，压板的下表面两侧边缘处均粘接有密封垫，U型框的正上方安装有盖板本体，安装组件包括侧板A和侧板B，侧板A和侧板B之间相对设置。本实用新型通过利用安装组件和扩张组件，在扭簧的弹性性能作用下带动卡板旋转并卡在凸板的下方，从而方便工作人员安装和拆卸，工作效率高，盖板本体受到卡板限制可避免其高度变化引起事故，同时在橡胶柱和弹簧的弹性性能作用下可对压板起到缓冲和减震的作用，且可以加快水流速度和体量。

title_localized.text: 家庭牧场用移动式草原粪拾捡收集装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了家庭牧场用移动式草原粪拾捡收集装置，包括牵引架、牵引车体、牵引环以及独立辊轴，所述牵引架上设置有牵引环，所述牵引架通过牵引环与牵引车体连接，所述牵引架上设置有独立辊轴，所述独立辊轴与牵引车体的发动机轮轴连接；本实用新型的有益效果是，该家庭牧场用移动式草原粪拾捡收集装置，采用牵引车体牵引进行移动，同时通过旁支动力组件获得牵引车体的动力机构输出动力，进而将动力均匀分配给循环式筛拣机构以及粉碎储存结构，从而实现了将草场上的粪便进行捡拾到粉碎后进行储存，便于后期回收利用，不仅捡拾效率高，工作区域呈指数级增加，同时结构简单紧凑，便于后期维护。

title_localized.text: 一种吹填软土地基的加固结构
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了建筑技术领域的一种吹填软土地基的加固结构，包括软土地基和硬土地基，硬土地基位于软土地基的底部，软土地基靠近硬土地基的底部设置有混凝土浇筑底板，混凝土浇筑底板的顶部固定连接有排水层，排水层的内壁固定连接有侧壁支撑板，侧壁支撑板的内壁开设有底端填充层，底端填充层的顶端内壁设置有格栅板，格栅板的顶部设置有下褥垫层，下褥垫层的顶部设置有土木格栅层。通过侧壁支撑板对侧壁形成支撑，配合顶部的格栅板、下褥垫层、土木格栅层和上褥垫层配合使用，为会回填层形成支撑，从而确保回填层的稳定性，同时通过底端填充层及内部的填充材料配合混凝土支撑柱为格栅板形成支撑，确保结构的整体强度和稳定性。

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及采掘机械化装备技术领域，且公开了一种帮锚杆钻车，包括底座，底座的上表面设有升降板，底座上表面一端两侧中部的圆形槽内均固定连接有第一套筒，第一套筒远离底座一端的中部活动套接有第一活动杆，第一活动杆远离第一套筒的一端固定连接在升降板的下表面，底座上表面远离第一套筒一侧中部的圆形槽内固定连接有第二套筒，第二活动杆远离第二套筒的一端固定连接在升降板的下表面，底座靠近第二套筒的一侧设有铲斗，在使用该帮锚杆钻车时，需要调节钻头的角度时，启动第二套筒，从而使第二活动杆在第二套筒的内部上升或者是下降，从而带动升降板靠近钻头的一端上升或者是下降，有利于实现钻头角度的调节。

title_localized.text: Submersible pump overflowing part sealing structure for well
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a immersible pump overflows component seal structure for well, including the rubber seal body, it strengthens the inserts to have the round in the rubber seal body, strengthen the inserts and strengthen the inserts for L shape, the rubber seal body inner circle is big-end-up's conical surface setting, and the last indent of rubber seal body is provided with round choked flow groove, and choked flow groove separates the rubber seal body inner circle for upper sealing face and lower sealing face. The inner ring of the rubber sealing body of the utility model is provided with a conical surface with a large upper part and a small lower part, so that the friction contact surface with the impeller is reduced, a circle of flow blocking groove is arranged inwards on the inner ring of the rubber sealing body, the flow blocking groove reduces friction, and simultaneously, the water flow impact force is reduced, and the rubber sealing body is combined with an upper sealing surface to play a main water blocking sealing role, and a lower sealing surface reduces contact friction to play an auxiliary water blocking sealing role, so that the power of the water pump is improved; the L-shaped reinforcing insert increases the strength of the product and prevents deformation; the notch is arranged to further reduce the contact friction between the notch and the impeller and improve the power of the water pump.

abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型公开了一种井用潜水泵过流部件密封结构，包括橡胶密封体，橡胶密封体内包覆有一圈加强嵌件，所述加强嵌件为L形加强嵌件，橡胶密封体内圈呈上大下小的锥面设置，橡胶密封体内圈上内凹设置有一圈阻流槽，阻流槽将橡胶密封体内圈分隔为上层密封面和下层密封面。本实用新型的橡胶密封体内圈呈上大下小的锥面设置，减少与叶轮的摩擦接触面，橡胶密封体内圈上内凹设置有一圈阻流槽，阻流槽减少摩擦，同时减缓水流冲力，结合上层密封面，起主要阻水密封作用，下层密封面减少接触摩擦，起辅助阻水密封作用，提升水泵功率；L形加强嵌件增加产品强度，防止变形；槽口的设置进一步减少与叶轮间的接触摩擦，提升水泵功率。

title_localized.text: 一种防爆轴流风机
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型属于轴流风机技术领域，尤其为一种防爆轴流风机，其包括防爆外壳体，所述防爆外壳体的内部设置有防爆电机，所述防爆电机通过四个防爆限位杆与防爆外壳体固定连接，所述防爆电机输出轴固定安装有叶片，所述防爆外壳体的下方设置有底座，所述防爆外壳体的下表面固定安装有四个活动杆，所述底座内部开设有活动槽所述活动槽的内部固定安装有套筒，所述套筒的内部设置有第一缓冲弹簧。需要说明的是，在本实用新型中，通过在防爆外壳体的外侧设置散热组件，使得散热组件中的散热风机在防爆电机运行停止后，对防爆电机起到一个散热的作用，避免了由于防爆电机长时间运行过热而发生故障或者爆炸现象的发生，故增加了装置使用时的安全性能。

abstract_localized.text: An automatic inflation system and an inflation box integrating the system relate to the technical field of inflation, wherein the automatic inflation system comprises a control device, and an air source input interface, a one-way valve, a pressure reducing valve, an emergency hand valve, an electric proportional valve, an inflation electromagnetic valve and an inflation interface which are connected in series through an air pipe; a gas cylinder hand valve and an air inlet pressure gauge are connected between the one-way valve and the pressure reducing valve, and the gas cylinder hand valve is connected with a gas storage cylinder; a primary pressure gauge is connected between the emergency hand valve and the electric proportional valve; a first pressure sensor is connected between the electric proportional valve and the inflation electromagnetic valve; a second pressure sensor is connected between the inflation electromagnetic valve and the inflation interface; the inflation box comprises a box body and a box cover, the box body comprises an inner cavity and a mounting panel, and all parts of the automatic inflation system are arranged and integrated on the upper plate surface of the mounting panel; the automatic inflation system and the inflation box integrated with the same can meet the inflation requirements of various devices to be inflated, are convenient to carry and high in automation degree, and can improve the working efficiency and the inflation safety.

abstract_localized.text: The utility model relates to a cultural product show field specifically discloses a product display device, including the show shelf, the internally mounted of show shelf has the lifting lead screw, the lower extreme of lifting lead screw is connected with driving motor, the lead screw slider has been cup jointed in the outside of lifting lead screw, get the below position of a cabinet door in the internally mounted of show shelf has down travel switch, get the lower extreme outside of a cabinet door and install magnetism and inhale the piece, down travel switch with be connected with the corotation wire between the driving motor, go up travel switch with be connected with the reversal wire between the driving motor. Transparent fender cover can carry out free installation and dismantlement in the upper end of show shelf through the screw thread draw-in groove, and the show can avoid being bumped by the mistake or stained under the protection of transparent fender cover at the article of sample backing plate top, and the whole inside lift of sample all is in the closed condition, guarantees the security of show in-process.

title_localized.text: 一种产品展示装置
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型涉及文化产品展示领域，具体公开了一种产品展示装置，包括展示架，所述展示架的内部安装有抬升丝杆，所述抬升丝杆的下端连接有驱动电机，所述抬升丝杆的外侧套接有丝杆滑块，所述取件柜门的下方位于所述展示架的内部安装有下行程开关，所述取件柜门的下端外侧安装有磁吸块，所述下行程开关与所述驱动电机之间连接有正转导线，所述上行程开关与所述驱动电机之间连接有反转导线。透明挡罩可以通过螺纹卡槽在展示架的上端进行自由的安装和拆卸，展示在样品垫板上方的物品可以在透明挡罩的防护下避免被误碰或是污损，且样品整体在的内部升降都处于封闭状态，保证展示过程中的安全性。

title_localized.text: Heating stirring cup with disinfection bowl cover
abstract_localized.text: The utility model discloses a heating and stirring cup with a disinfection cup cover, which comprises a cup body and a cup cover arranged on the cup body, wherein a stirring piece which can be driven to rotate and stir the liquid in the cup body is arranged in the cup body; realize the stirring through stirring spare and drive arrangement, keep invariable temperature through heating device, disinfect in to the cup through the ultraviolet lamp that disinfects, make the cup break away from first base can the exclusive use stir and heating function through setting up energy storage component in the cup, it is more convenient to use.

title_localized.text: 一种具有消毒杯盖的加热搅拌杯
abstract_localized.text: 本实用新型所公开的一种具有消毒杯盖的加热搅拌杯，包括杯体及盖设于杯体上的杯盖，所述杯体内设置有可被驱动旋转而对杯体内液体进行搅拌的搅拌件，所述杯体上安装有加热装置，所述杯盖上朝向杯体容置腔的一侧面安装有杀菌紫外灯以用于对杯体容置腔进行杀菌消毒；通过搅拌件与驱动装置实现搅拌，通过加热装置保持恒定水温，通过杀菌紫外灯对杯体内进行杀菌，通过在杯体内设置储能组件使得杯体脱离第一底座可以单独使用搅拌和加热功能，使用更加便捷。
inventor_harmonized.name: YU YIZE
